remarks.format: ## Remarks 使用類別以程式設計方式管理的集合物件表示中的單一資料列的儲存格控制項。Use the class to programmatically manage a collection of objects that represent the cells of a single row in an control. 這個類別常用來新增、 移除或修改的資料列中的資料格的內容控制項。This class is commonly used to add, remove, or modify the contents of a cell in a row of an control. > [!NOTE] > 控制項包含屬性，其中包含的集合物件。An control contains a property that contains a collection of objects. 每個物件都代表資料表中的個別資料列。Each object represents an individual row in the table. 物件包含所表示的集合屬性物件。An object contains a property that represents a collection of objects. 這些物件，代表個別儲存格的資料列。These objects, in turn, represent the individual cells of a row. 若要擷取個別的資料格，請先取得物件，表示包含資料表中的資料格的資料列 (從的集合控制項)。To retrieve an individual cell, first get the object that represents the row containing the cell in the table (from the collection of the control). 您可以取得物件，表示資料列中的資料格 (來自的集合物件)。You can then get the object that represents the cell in the row (from the collection of the object). ## Examples 下列程式碼範例示範如何以動態方式產生的內容控制項加入儲存格大小以集合。The following code example demonstrates how to dynamically generate the contents of an control by adding cells to an collection. 請注意，屬性所表示列物件，是集合。Notice that the property of a row, represented by an object, is the collection.
